<topic template="Default" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title translate="true">Simple Model: Recharge</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Simple Model: Recharge</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The model has a uniform recharge rate of 3e-8 ft/s. &#160;On the top view of the model, </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Creating_Objects" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">create a Rectangle object</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> that completely surrounds the grid. &#160;In the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Object_Properties_Dialog_Box" styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Object Properties</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box, switch to the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">MODFLOW Features</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> tab and check the check box for the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">RCH</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> package. Enter a </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Starting time</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> of 0, an </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Ending time</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> of 86400 and a </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Recharge rate</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> of 3E-8. Click </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">OK</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> to close the dialog box.</text></para>
  </body>
</topic>
